s agent (2 relations)\n- Infrastructure agent (2 relations)\n- Rollback agent (2 relations)\n- Communication agent (2 relations)\n- Workload systems (4 relations)\n\nCount: 10", "answer": [13], "metadata": {"type": "fill_in_the_blank", "sub_type": "entities_have_more_than_one_relations", "difficulty": "basic"}, "setting": {"model": "claude-haiku-4-5", "temperature": 0, "flag_async": true, "max_completion_tokens": 512, "requests_per_minute": 50, "max_concurrency": 5, "max_retries": 6, "base_backoff_s": 0.8, "max_backoff_s": 20.0}, "token_usage": {"prompt_tokens": 1964, "completion_tokens": 512, "total_tokens": 2476}}
